author: veithen
msg: Merged OMNavigator (LLOM) and DOMNavigator (DOOM) into a single class in axiom-api. These classes were almost identical. Only the code accessing the first child of a container and the next sibling of a node without advancing the parser was implementation specific, but this can be better achieved by adding methods for this to OMContainerEx and OMNodeEx.
